**[tools]**

---

```json
[
  {
    "type": "function",
    "function": {
      "name": "predict_commute_time",
      "description": "This function predicts the commute time for a user based on historical commute data, weather conditions, and traffic conditions.",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "user_id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Unique identifier for the user.",
            "minLength": 1,
            "maxLength": 50
